 1280, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m freestyle\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite a lack of top-level experience, Ledecky was the youngest member of the United States team at the London Games.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999988803919578, \"rank\": 6.75231148760784e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"top-level experience\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngest member\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"the London Games\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was there that she gained international recognition,winning the 800m freestyle gold, and smashing a 23-year-old American record in the process.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999286913335713, \"rank\": 5.7449633281697215e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"international recognition\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m freestyle gold\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 800m gold was Ledecky's first senior international medal of her career, a rare feat for someone yet to enter their final year of school.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 800m gold\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky's first senior international medal\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"a rare feat\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"their final year\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky has always held a love for her sport and has consistently pushed herself further.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"a love\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of her most memorable quotes was whenshe said: \\\"I try to make the good days great and take something positive from the days I am not feeling good.\\\"\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her most memorable quotes\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"whenshe\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"the good days\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rio 2016 also came before Ledecky had started at Stanford University, her place having been strategically deferred for a year to allow for full focus on the Games.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"score\": 0.9999999242752466, \"rank\": 7.572452051355364e-08, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"her place\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"full focus\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Rio,Ledecky's medal haul put her in a class above.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1557074834422335e-14, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky's medal haul\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"a class\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished the games with four gold medals, a silver medal, and an 800m world record.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"four gold medals\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"an 800m world record\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky became the first swimmer since 1968 to win the 200, 400 and 800m freestyle at the same Olympics, and also most decorated United States female athlete at a single games.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999988803919578, \"rank\": 6.75231148760784e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2351}, {\"ngram\": \"the first swimmer\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200, 400 and 800m freestyle\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"the same Olympics\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"a single games\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Phelps had more medals from Rio, with five golds and one silver.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.5018410262851236e-11, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 2554, \"end\": 2557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1557074834422335e-14, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more medals\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"five golds\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"one silver\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tokyo was not quite as prolific for Ledecky, although she left the pandemic-hit Games with two gold medals and two silvers, she also suffered her first loss in an individual event at the Olympics, her previous silver had come from a relay.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2592, \"end\": 2597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9599796489266812, \"rank\": 0.041688737142950794, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prolific\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic-hit Games\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"two gold medals\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"two silvers\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"her first loss\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual event\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"her previous silver\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"a relay\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's 1500m freestyle race was a new event for the Summer Olympics, although the men's had been introduced four years previously, and Ledecky went on to become the first woman to be awarded that gold medal.\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The women's 1500m freestyle race\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"a new event\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"the first woman\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold medal\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky's success is at least in part due to her attitude, she said,reported by theAssociated Press: \\\"I am pretty tough on myself,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky's success\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"her attitude\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"theAssociated Press\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I think I have found the balance of being tough on myself but also having that grace.\\\"\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the balance\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"that grace\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In all her years of competition, Ledecky is the only swimmer to win five consecutive world titles in an individual event, the 800m freestyle, an event which she has dominated for over a decade.\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all her years\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"the only swimmer\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"five consecutive world titles\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual event\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m freestyle\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3432}, {\"ngram\": \"over a decade\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has broken 14 world and 37 national records, and will want to stand on the podium again at theParis 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"14 world\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"37 national records\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having burst onto the scene as a teenager, Ledecky is now 27 and potentially competing for a final time on the Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3645}, {\"ngram\": \"a final time\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3698}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then again, the Los Angeles Games in 2028 might be too tempting to miss as an all-time great looks to write more history on home soil.\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3737, \"end\": 3748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999856199803, \"rank\": 1.397618303225773e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an all-time great looks\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3819}, {\"ngram\": \"more history\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"home soil\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 4087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3908, \"end\": 3919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999996980478, \"rank\": 1.9767013457809977e-10, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3893}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3949}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4001}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4070}]}]}"